description: Apocalyptico Aiotart is a limited collection of digital collectibles and brings these NFTs right onto the Tangle to be part of what is moving the future in a positive direction through low energy consumption the use of invative technolgies. Each NFT is unique and created from hand-picked photos of my collection. All NFTs show the consequences of the environment pollution, depleted and overpopulated earth in the future as science fiction. These have been transformed into masterpieces through the use of artificial intelligence. There will only be a limit of three editions of the artworks. Take the chance to get one of these nice NFTs from the Sci-Fi collection.
name: Apocalyptico Aiotart
